SELECT 
    u.[Id],
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE u.[CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN urd.[CreatedOn] IS NULL THEN GETDATE()
		ELSE urd.[CreatedOn]
	  END AS [CreatedOn],
    urd.UserId,
    ua.AgencyId, 
    STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') AS Roles,
    CASE 
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%System Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial Reporter%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Agency Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Analyst%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Manager%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister Assistant%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Executive Director%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%View Only Properties%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002'
	   
    END AS UserType
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        ur.UserId,
        MAX(ur.CreatedOn) AS CreatedOn,
        STRING_AGG(r.Name, ', ') AS RoleName
    FROM [pims].[dbo].[UserRoles] ur
    INNER JOIN Roles r ON ur.RoleId = r.Id
    GROUP BY ur.UserId
) AS urd ON u.Id = urd.UserId

LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT UserId, MIN(AgencyId) AS AgencyId
    FROM UserAgencies
    GROUP BY UserId
) ua_min ON u.Id = ua_min.UserId
LEFT OUTER JOIN UserAgencies ua ON u.Id = ua.UserId AND ua.AgencyId = ua_min.AgencyId

WHERE u.Id <> '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
GROUP BY u.[Id],
    u.[CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    urd.CreatedOn, 
    urd.UserId, 
    ua.AgencyId
ORDER BY urd.CreatedOn ASC;

SELECT p.[Id],
    p.[CreatedById],
    p.[CreatedOn],
    p.[UpdatedById],
    p.[UpdatedOn],
    p.[Name],
    p.[Description],
    p.[ClassificationId],
    p.[AgencyId],
    p.[IsSensitive],
    p.[IsVisibleToOtherAgencies],
    p.[PID],
    p.[PIN],
    p.[LandArea],
    p.[LandLegalDescription],
    p.[Zoning],
    p.[ZoningPotential],
    p.[NotOwned],
	CONVERT(VARCHAR(40), CAST(Location.Long AS DECIMAL(18, 14))) + ', ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR(40), CAST(Location.Lat AS DECIMAL(18, 14))) AS Location,
	aa.Id as AdministrativeAreaId,
	a.Address1, 
	a.Postal
FROM 
    [pims].[dbo].[Parcels] p
	INNER JOIN Addresses a
	ON p.AddressId = a.Id
	INNER JOIN AdministrativeAreas aa
	ON aa.Name = a.AdministrativeArea
WHERE aa.Id NOT IN (

SELECT Id
FROM AdministrativeAreas a
WHERE a.Name NOT IN (
SELECT [Name]
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[AdminAreaswithRegionalDistricts]
  )
  and a.Name NOT LIKE '%District%' and a.Name NOT LIKE '%Test%'
) AND aa.Id NOT IN (94, 78, 288, 2478, 2479)
AND aa.Id <= 500 -- limit it so we're not importing parcels whose admin area is a regional district

SELECT b.Id, CAST('2023-01-17 17:58:40.246' AS datetime)
 as CreatedOn, null as UpdatedOn, ar.Name, 0 as IsDisabled, 0 as SortOrder, null as Abbreviation, null as BoundaryType, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' as CreatedById, null as UpdatedById, a.Id AS RD_Id
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[AdminAreaswithRegionalDistricts] ar
  LEFT OUTER JOIN AdministrativeAreas a
  ON ar.RD_NAME = a.Name
 LEFT OUTER JOIN AdministrativeAreas b
 ON b.Name = ar.Name
  WHERE ar.RD_NAME <> '0' and b.Id >= 1
  ORDER BY ar.Name

SELECT a.Id, CAST('2023-01-17 17:58:40.246' AS datetime)
 as CreatedOn, null as UpdatedOn, ar.Name, 0 as IsDisabled, 0 as SortOrder, null as Abbreviation, null as BoundaryType, '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000' as CreatedById, null as UpdatedById, ar.Regional_District, b.Id AS RD_Id
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[AdminAreasCurrentlyInPIMS_RDsImported] ar

 LEFT OUTER JOIN AdministrativeAreas b
 ON b.Name = ar.Regional_District
ORDER By a.Name

SELECT 
    u.[Id],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE u.[CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    urd.CreatedOn,
    urd.UserId,
    ua.AgencyId, 
    STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') AS Roles,
    CASE 
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%System Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial Reporter%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Agency Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Analyst%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Manager%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister Assistant%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Executive Director%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%View Only Properties%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002'
	   
    END AS UserType
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        ur.UserId,
        MAX(ur.CreatedOn) AS CreatedOn,
        STRING_AGG(r.Name, ', ') AS RoleName
    FROM [pims].[dbo].[UserRoles] ur
    INNER JOIN Roles r ON ur.RoleId = r.Id
    GROUP BY ur.UserId
) AS urd ON u.Id = urd.UserId

LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT UserId, MIN(AgencyId) AS AgencyId
    FROM UserAgencies
    GROUP BY UserId
) ua_min ON u.Id = ua_min.UserId
LEFT OUTER JOIN UserAgencies ua ON u.Id = ua.UserId AND ua.AgencyId = ua_min.AgencyId

WHERE u.Id <> '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'

GROUP BY u.[Id],
    u.[CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    urd.CreatedOn, 
    urd.UserId, 
    ua.AgencyId
ORDER BY urd.CreatedOn ASC

		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Kent' THEN 439
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Highlands' THEN 348
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Slocan' THEN 380
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Warfield' THEN 448
        ELSE aa.Id 
    END AS AdministrativeAreaId,  
	a.AdministrativeArea,
	a.Address1, 
	a.Postal,
	pp.ParcelId as ParentID,
	0 as PropertyTypeID
FROM 
    [pims].[dbo].[Parcels] p
	INNER JOIN Addresses a
	ON p.AddressId = a.Id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN AdministrativeAreas aa
	ON aa.Name = a.AdministrativeArea
    LEFT OUTER JOIN ParcelParcels pp
    ON pp.SubdivisionId = p.Id
